\c 2
\s Ninivhe richaparadzwa naJehovha
\p
\v 1 Muputsanyi wakwira pamberi pechiso chako, chengetedza nhare, rinda nzira, simbisa chiuno, simbisa masimba zvakasimba.
\v 2 Nokuti Jehovha anodzosa ukuru hwaJakove seukuru hwaIsraeri. Nokuti vanovadurura vakavadurura ndokuparadza matavi emizambiringa yavo.
\v 3 Nhovo dzemhare dzake dzakatsvukiswa, varume vakatsunga vakapfeka zvitsvuku; ngoro dziri mukati nemoto wedare pazuva rekuzvigadzirira kwake, nemiti yemifiri ichazungunuswa.
\v 4 Ngoro dzinopenga munzira dzemumusha, dzinoenda uko neuko pamapani, kuonekwa kwadzo kwakaita semwenje, dzinomhanya semheni.
\v 5 Acharangarira vakuru vake, vachagumburwa pakufamba kwavo, uye vachakurumidza parusvingo rwavo, chitaviriro chamiswa.
\v 6 Masuwo enzizi achazarurwa, uye muzinda uchanyauka.
\v 7 Zvino Huzabhi achaiswa muutapwa, achakwidzwa, uye varandakadzi vake vachamutungamirira sezvinoita neshoko renjiva.
\v 8 Asi Ninivhe rakaita sedziva remvura kubva kare; zvakadaro vachatiza, vachiti: Mirai! Mirai! Asi hakuna achadzoka.
\v 9 Pambai sirivha, pambai goridhe; nokuti hakuna mugumo wezvakaunganidzwa, kubwinya kwenhumbi dzinoshuviwa.
\v 10 Harina chinhu, harichashandi, raparara; moyo unonyauka, nemabvi anorovana, nemarwadzo makuru ari pazviuno zvese, nezviso zvavo vese zvacheneruka.
\p
\v 11 Huripi ugaro hweshumbakadzi, nenzvimbo yekudyira yeshumba diki iripi, paifamba shumba, shumba huru nembwanana yeshumba, uye pasina anodzityityidzira?
\v 12 Shumba yaibvamburanya zvakaringana imbwanana dzayo, ndokudzipira shumbakadzi yayo, ndokuzadza gara rayo nezvakapambiwa, nenzvimbo dzayo dzekugara nezvakabvamburwa.
\p
\v 13 Tarira, ndinopikisana newe, anoreva Jehovha wehondo, ndichapisa ngoro dzako muutsi, uye munondo uchapedza hando dzeshumba dzako, uye ndichagura zvakapambiwa zvako kubva panyika, neshoko revatumwa vako haringanzwikwi.